title: X Factor: Nathanael Landskroner tries to conquer his nerves and a Whitney Houston classic - The X Factor Reality TV -
text: Always a classic, the contestants on The X Factor are breaking out the Whitney Houston songs as the Six Chair Challenges continue.Latest to perform is Nathanael Landskroner, who takes on 'I Have Nothing' - but will his nerves get the better of him? Watch a teaser here:X Factor: The 5 most performed songs that just won't go awayHe tells his mentor Nick Grimshaw he has chosen the song because "he hasn't given [his] all yet" and adds: "I feel like I've got to take a risk or I'm going home."But within seconds of starting, he's visibly shaking, with Cheryl Fernandez-Versini telling the panel: "He's terrified... terrified."Nathanael loses his words, but can he pull the performance back?Watch his performance in full on The X Factor on Sunday, October 11 on ITV1 at 7pm.
